data.description: MOVE-IN-READY. Welcome Home to your quiet and friendly neighborhood! This beautiful home has 4 bedrooms/2 baths and a 24x24 detached garage/workshop with a large loft for storage. It's on a double wooded lot just shy of an acre! Beautiful views. Deck has been recently stained. Dehumidifier in the Crawl Space. Open floor plan. Lots of natural light.  Nice size bedrooms with walk in closets. Double sinks in the Primary bathroom off of the large Primary bedroom and check out that spacious closet! Huge laundry with shelving.  New flooring, new 55 gallon Water heater, new HVAC. Propane Tank is full.
